{-| Helpers can be set in the config type.

There are two kinds of helpers:

  - (Expression) Helpers `{{helper a b c}}`
  - (Block) Helpers `{{#helper a}} content {{/helper}}`


# Expression Helper

@docs lookup, equals


# Block Helper

@docs if_, unless, inline, inside

-}

